{"tid":1956376,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"支那中山大學打壓言論自由 減經費威脅學生禁言","createTime":"2020-04-03T06:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T07:48:31.000Z","uid":345042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"31c8f8667a4f50abb7bb5c0550062222de68ac27","tid":1956376,"uid":345042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTwFmPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTwFmPB.jpg&h=a2e2124a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTAF6gh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTAF6gh.jpg&h=09bd31a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣州中山大學停課超過兩個月，部分院校陸陸續續開設網課。但最近開設網課的院校突然暫停所有網課課程，原因是學校不承認網課課程，學生仍然要等待學校通告才能重新教學。由於學生們對學校零通知感到不滿，有學生在微信朋友圈發表評論，批評學校兩個月內沒有任何教學通知。評論在校內廣泛流傳，使學校教務老師主動聯絡學生，要求刪除有關留言，否則刪減學院經費及保研名額。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可憐嘅支那大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baffd67a0e40596115b149c22ea94b1bb4fd9f65","tid":1956376,"uid":203909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"原來屌學校做野做得廢都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426d710ab593cbd511cc73fd454d18f1893e9ba0","tid":1956376,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:48:31.000Z","msg":"不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「解悶工廠」 點解還押抗爭者仲睇到連登？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1956428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1956428</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}